How do you get started?

Chaos engineering: injecting precise and measured amounts of harm to a system for the purpose of improving the systems reliability

Evolve CE along with other best practices
* observability
* monitoring / alerting
* incident response
* blameless postmortems

incidents - unplanned investments in companies' survival
CE - planned investments ...
ROI - understanding/learning
turn chaos into stories and complete them

